{"tid":1715472,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【抗暴之戰】教局急召十八區校長開會 消息：下午或宣佈明、後天停課","createTime":"2019-11-13T06:02:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T06:29:41.000Z","uid":212626,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"80e08490600cf333f7e45d867239a14f2323973f","tid":1715472,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T06:02:00.000Z","msg":"教育局政治凌駕學子安危堅拒停課，觸怒學界。消息指，教育局近日一直迴避學校查詢及追問，有教育局分區主任竟向學校稱「中央（指教育局總部）無指示」，僅要求各校校董會自行決定停課。《蘋果》獲悉，教育局今早急召十八區中學校長會主席會面，料商討停課問題；消息指，教育局最快於下午3時發新聞稿宣佈明、後日（14日、15日）停課。  <br />\n<br />\n據悉，全港多區中小學已經自行決定明、後兩天自行停課，或者取消原有活動，部分學校如培正中學已經發對家長及學生發通告，培正通告宣佈明、後兩天停課，下周一（11月18日）補假，即學生最快下周二才重返校園；而大埔三育中學今日已停課一天，原定後日（15日）舉行的秋季旅行亦將改為回校上課。據悉，不少目前尚未發通告的學校，亦正在積極考慮，有校長說：「聽日（14日）就一定要停，後日仍然在考慮，但初步睇相當多學校傾向停兩日，再觀望周末情況。」  <br />\n<br />\n教育局無能、學界只能「自己學生自己救」。有校長對教育局態度極度不滿，怒斥教育局局長楊潤雄欠缺承擔，「因為（特首）林鄭（月娥）唔可以中圈套，就要學生冒險，要學校同校董會自己孭飛，呢個咩道理？好多校長都好憤怒。」另有中學校長直指對林鄭政府徹底失望，指學界在7月、8月會見林鄭及民政事務局局長劉江華，一早明確要求立即徹回修例及獨立調查，如果政府從善如流，或不致今天局面。  <br />\n<br />\n中學校長會今日下午2時半將開記者會，惟校長會主席鄧振強拒絕於會前透露詳情。 <br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191113/60261656\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191113%2F60261656&d=lZ7jQHZQyV3jEURUmMbLaSvt59O44HeJS3%2BtxtDyp5g%3D&h=1d77f391\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191113%2F60261656&h=9cdf3908\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20191113/60261656</a>"},{"pid":"550fa3736d35b4ac7d3f3ff90a501f91304acd5c","tid":1715472,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T06:04:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f17f954c770ae503258ac5aff3352b69347540b","tid":1715472,"uid":38904,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T06:04:37.000Z","msg":"教育局以下犯上暗示社會停擺?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n#讉責教育局"},{"pid":"1ec77d42444f1598d805a65fc1e4a3ee557c81a8","tid":1715472,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T06:06:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11315805a9bde02e78428013936640d3ee26aaf2","tid":1715472,"uid":262342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f17f954c770ae503258ac5aff3352b69347540b","tid":1715472,"uid":38904,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T06:04:37.000Z","msg":"教育局以下犯上暗示社會停擺?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n#讉責教育局"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T06:07:21.000Z","msg":"教育局帶頭中計"},{"pid":"cb2912ed0f9ca72456229a78b97ff5afb1b95b26","tid":1715472,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T06:08:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"037020884246eaa0c6c9b3bbdf9db9b501138eec","tid":1715472,"uid":71620,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T06:08:47.000Z","msg":"幾時到勞工處同僱主開會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee490a481c8b4be51e1b2f1c4600bf34d64a4cca","tid":1715472,"uid":49853,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T06:08:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/lamcheng-06_pDEKY_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Flamcheng-06_pDEKY_1200x0.png&h=a98804d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n墮入圈套<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f111bd771fde66a168a2356d28c55ec617f7a076","tid":1715472,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee490a481c8b4be51e1b2f1c4600bf34d64a4cca","tid":1715472,"uid":49853,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":